messages.content: what are the tracks for digital arts

The tracks available in the Faculty of Digital Arts and Design include:

1. Animation Arts
2. User Experience Design
3. Digital Interior Design
4. Game Design
5. Graphic and Media Design (starting soon)
6. Interaction Design Arts (starting soon)
7. New Media Arts (starting soon)

For more information, you can explore the [Faculty of Digital Arts and Design](https://eui.edu.eg/faculty-digital-arts-and-design/home).
who are the professors at the faculty of business informatics

The specific professors at the Faculty of Business Informatics are not detailed on the site. However, it mentions that Prof. Mohamed Saleh is the Dean of the Faculty. For more information about the faculty members, you may need to explore further sections of the website or contact the institution directly. 

For more details about the faculty, you can visit the faculty's home page: [Faculty of Business Informatics](https://eui.edu.eg/faculty-business-informatics/home).
who are the professors at the faculty of computer science

The professors at the Faculty of Computing and Information Sciences include:

- Prof. Mohamed El-Sharkawi, Professor of Data Science and Engineering
- Dr. Amal Elgammal, Head of the Software Engineering Department
- Dr. Amany H.B. Eissa, Head of EUI's Entrepreneurship and Innovation Center

For more details, you can visit [EUI Founders](https://eui.edu.eg/eui-founders).
